10.8|0|9.8|%31.4 @Fri @Sep @13 @10:00:00 @1986 
11|5.5|9.9|%36.4 @Fri @Sep @14 @00:20:00 @1985 
5.1|3.9|10|%28.4 @Fri @Sep @15 @00:00:30 @1984
