</LI>
<LI>Understand how untagged attributes are interpreted (as string
attributes);
</LI>
<LI>Know when to call <TT>G_site_get_fmt()</TT> and how to get
<EM>all</EM> fields from a site record; and
</LI>
<LI>Know how to read and write a site file.
